back.description:
When you **_feed the satchel 1 Surplus of freshly_** **_harvested foodstuffs_**, it fits even though it should not. Until next autumn’s harvest, the satchel will provide 1 use of provisions each day. They are fresh and nourishing, but different each time (and not at all what you fed the satchel).

**1d6** today’s food is...

@DrawTableInline[Compendium.stonetop.wonder-tables.RollTable.zKCaEYu3bUkn3A7p]{1d6}

When you **_draw more than 1 use of provisions_** **_from the satchel in a given day_**, it provides up to 10 uses but will produce no more until you feed it again next autumn.
